Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.54,0:01:48.55,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¡No! ¡Suéltame!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.76,0:01:50.88,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¡Cálmate!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.51,0:01:53.93,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,No soy tu enemigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.51,0:01:56.42,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Por favor, cálmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.93,0:02:01.93,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Aqua… Pero ¿por qué?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:06.98,Cart_A_Tim,CARTEL,0,0,0,,{\fs12\xshad-2\blur0.7\fax0.3\c&H162944&\3c&H384568&\frz343.9\pos(218.494,136)\4c&H1C253D&}Kurokawa
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:07.10,Cart_A_Tim,CARTEL,0,0,0,,{\fs12\xshad-2\blur0.7\fax0.3\c&H162944&\3c&H384568&\frz343.9\pos(218.494,136)\4c&H1C253D&\clip(m 224 136 l 221 140 219 145 217 153 177 151 188 117)}Kurokawa
